#. type: expansion
#: sections/card_effect_keywords.tex:157
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\vspace*{1em}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{Force Field Token}{\\subsection*{Force Field Token}}\n"
"  \\index{Force Field}\n"
"  \\setlength\\intextsep{0pt}\n"
"  \\setlength\\columnsep{1em}\n"
"  \\begin{wrapfigure}{r}{0.25\\linewidth}\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=4.6em]{\\images/force-field-token.png}\n"
"    \\begin{center}\n"
"      \\imagecaption{Force Field Token}\\\\\n"
"      \\vspace*{1em}\n"
"    \\end{center}\n"
"  \\end{wrapfigure}\n"
"  Use the \\textbf{Force Field Token} to mark the effect of the \\wikilink{spells/force_field}{\\textbf{Force Field Spell}.}\n"
"  The Token represents an Obstacle, so only \\svg{unit_flying} units can move through a space with this Token.\n"
"  If you're using the normal Combat Board, place 1 Force Field Token.\n"
"  If you're using the \\pagelink{Battlefield Combat}{Battlefield Board}, place 2 Tokens on two adjacent spaces.\n"
"\\begin{center}\n"
"  {\\hspace{2em}\\transparent{0.2}\\includegraphics[width=0.5\\linewidth]{\\art/land_mine.png}}\n"
"\\end{center}"
msgstr ""
"  \\vspace*{1em}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{Force Field Token}{\\subsection*{力墙标记}}\n"
"  \\index{力墙}\n"
"  \\setlength\\intextsep{0pt}\n"
"  \\setlength\\columnsep{1em}\n"
"  \\begin{wrapfigure}{r}{0.25\\linewidth}\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=4.6em]{\\images/force-field-token.png}\n"
"    \\begin{center}\n"
"      \\imagecaption{力墙标记}\\\\\n"
"      \\vspace*{1em}\n"
"    \\end{center}\n"
"  \\end{wrapfigure}\n"
"  使用\\textbf{力墙标记}来标记\\wikilink{spells/force_field}{\\textbf{大力神盾}}的效果。%\n"
"  该标记代表一个障碍物，因此只有\\svg{unit_flying}单位可以穿越带有此标记的位置。%\n"
"  如果你使用普通战斗板，放置1个力墙标记。%\n"
"  如果你使用\\pagelink{Battlefield Combat}{战场板}，在两个相邻位置上放置2个标记。\n"
"\\begin{center}\n"
"  {\\hspace{2em}\\transparent{0.2}\\includegraphics[width=0.5\\linewidth]{\\art/land_mine.png}}\n"
"\\end{center}"

#. type: Plain text
#: sections/card_effect_keywords.tex:179
msgid "\\pagetarget{Summoning}{\\subheader{Summoning}\\index{Summoning}}"
msgstr "\\pagetarget{Summoning}{\\subheader{召唤}\\index{召唤}}"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/card_effect_keywords.tex:179
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{inferno,conflux}\n"
"  Summoned units activate in the Round they were summoned if their Initiative is lower than or equal to the Initiative of the currently activated unit.\n"
"  Otherwise, treat them as if they already activated this Combat Round."
msgstr ""
"{inferno,conflux}\n"
"  如果召唤单位的先攻值低于或等于当前激活单位的先攻值，它们会在被召唤的轮次内激活。%\n"
"  否则，将它们视为本战斗轮次已激活。"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/card_effect_keywords.tex:179
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{2}\n"
"  \\begin{expansion}{conflux}\n"
"    \\subsection*{Summon Elemental Units}\n"
"    The \\textbf{Summon Elemental Spells} allow you to add an Elemental unit to the Combat Board during Combat.\n"
"    Keep the Summoned Unit Deck face up near the Neutral Unit Decks.\n"
"    Depending on the \\svg{empower} used, you can Summon either a non-reinforced unit (a Few) or a reinforced one (a Pack).\n"
"    Take the corresponding unit card from the Summoned Unit Deck and place it on a chosen empty space.\n"
"    You may place \\textbf{Summon Unit Tokens} instead of the cards.\n"
"    When using the \\pagelink{Battlefield Combat}{Battlefield Board}, you must place the Token.\n"
"    Summoned units remain under your control until they perish or Combat ends.\n"
"    A Summoned Elemental Unit is \\textbf{not} added to your Unit Deck.\n"
"    \\bigskip\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{2}\n"
"  \\begin{expansion}{conflux}\n"
"    \\subsection*{召唤元素单位}\n"
"    \\textbf{召唤元素法术}允许你在战斗中将一个元素单位添加到战斗板上。%\n"
"    将召唤单位牌堆正面朝上放置在中立单位牌堆附近。%\n"
"    根据所使用的\\svg{empower}，你可以召唤一个未增援单位（少量）或一个已增援单位（一群）。%\n"
"    从召唤单位牌堆中取出对应的单位牌，并将其放置在一个选定的空位上。%\n"
"    你可以放置\\textbf{召唤单位标记}来代替这些牌。%\n"
"    当使用\\pagelink{Battlefield Combat}{战场板}时，你必须放置标记。%\n"
"    被召唤的单位在其死亡或战斗结束前由你控制。%\n"
"    召唤的元素单位\\textbf{不}会被加入你的单位牌堆。\n"
"    \\bigskip\n"
"\n"

